  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the air fryer to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Rinse the cod fillets and pat dry with paper towels.",
    "Season the cod with salt and pepper.",
    "Place the cod fillets in the air fryer basket, and cook for 8 minutes.",
    "In a large skillet, heat the milk over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced sweet potatoes, chopped onions, and chopped bell peppers to the skillet.",
    "Cook for 10 minutes, or until the sweet potatoes are tender.",
    "Flake the cooked cod into the skillet with the sweet potato mixture.",
    "Mix well to combine, and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, and enjoy!"
